title: I Have No Missions
body: I have no missions since the event ended what happened??{{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}}

replies.body: Which event do you mean?  [Versus ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/events/vs-2017)has been over for a bit.  You can obtain another set of missions, though, if you've unlocked Kayn.  I hope that helps clear things up!
i dont think there are anymore right now... i dont have any either so i think we will just have to wait for the next event...
